<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="197" type="male genitalia">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">Male genitalia.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="197">
Pygofer (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">13</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">14</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">16</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">17</figureCitation>
) symmetrical, gradually narrowed towards apex, with sinuate anterior and posterior margins. Pygopher with internal sulcus and almost parallel lateral margins in ventral view. Anal tube (Figs 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">13</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 9–19" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figures 9 - 19. Metanigrus chromus sp. nov., male 9 head and thorax, dorsal view 10 frons, ventral view 11 tegmina 12 wing 13, 16 pygofer, lateral view 14, 17 gonostyli and pygofer, ventral view 15 aedeagus, left lateral view 18 gonostyli, dorsal view 19 aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1024.62226.figures9-19" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/520804" pageId="0" pageNumber="197">16</figureCitation>
